1
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:29,350
Su Xia?

2
00:01:32,789 --> 00:01:33,680
Get them!

3
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,950
Su Xia...

4
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,120
Fan.

5
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,310
Untie me!

6
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,400
Bear with it.

7
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,350
Just a little longer.

8
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,110
Why are you laughing?

9
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,840
Thank you.

10
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,079
It's nothing.

11
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,950
Thank you for staying by my side.

12
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,970
I can do this myself.

13
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,000
I think...

14
00:02:58,310 --> 00:03:01,080
I can't keep my promise.

15
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,090
I can't keep my word.

16
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:08,630
Actually,

17
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,980
I'm happy with how things are now.

18
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,190
Qin.

19
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,590
Thanks for

20
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:57,710
handling my debt.

21
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,400
I'll never forget

22
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:02,810
what you did for me.

23
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,000
Fan.

24
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,310
Don't be so polite.

25
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,340
We've been friends for years.

26
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,680
I believe

27
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,670
you'll get back on your feet.

28
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:21,680
Forget it.

29
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,560
I'm afraid I can't.

30
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,070
But this is nice, actually.

31
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,750
Fan, what's wrong with you?

32
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,010
Where's your passion?

33
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,430
I know

34
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,240
you're upset

35
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,310
because you don't know
who stabbed you in the back.

36
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:41,920
You don't know the truth.

37
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:43,590
You don't know anything.

38
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,870
The truth?

39
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,480
Do you know something?

40
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,159
Hey, say something!

41
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,040
Please tell me!

42
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,240
Fan, calm down.

43
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,460
Just calm down.

44
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,190
I can tell you,

45
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,390
but don't seek revenge, okay?

46
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,750
Promise me

47
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,390
you'll stay calm

48
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,360
after I tell you.

49
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,120
Okay.

50
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,170
I'll stay calm.

51
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,390
Tell me.

52
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:24,560
The real mastermind
behind Lu Group's collapse

53
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,560
has been Xiao Qi all along.

54
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,630
Actually, it's because of Tang Group

55
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,360
and Tang Fei.

56
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,600
The one who profited the most

57
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,000
from Lu Group's collapse

58
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,130
was the Jian family.

59
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,360
Xiao Qi?

60
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,120
Tang Fei?

61
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,190
Yes.

62
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,390
Why...

63
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,420
I understand why Xiao Qi did this.

64
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:52,920
But who's Tang Fei?

65
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,040
Tang Fei

66
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,870
went bankrupt because of your father

67
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:57,750
and jumped off a building.

68
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:02,510
And Xiao Qi is Tang Fei's son.

69
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:03,840
His real name is Tang Qi.

70
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,630
All these years,

71
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,160
Xiao Qi has been hiding his identity

72
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,950
and enduring humiliation

73
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,510
just so that one day,

74
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,630
he could collect

75
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,070
this blood debt from you,

76
00:06:13,070 --> 00:06:14,800
your father, and the Lu family.

77
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,310
So, Su Xia is not

78
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,190
the only reason Xiao Qi hates you.

79
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:19,270
It's more because of the things

80
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,800
your father did to them.

81
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:25,830
Xiao Qi.

82
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,510
Tang Qi.

83
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,400
That's right.

84
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,310
Good.

85
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,430
Great.

86
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:41,159
I should pay for my father's sins,
and I get it.

87
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,720
But why did the Jians

88
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,120
betray me?

89
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:47,520
What do they have to do with Tang Group?

90
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,600
No.

91
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,870
Jian Xi, the Jian family...

92
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,680
They have to give me an explanation!

93
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,760
Where are you going?

94
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,920
How's your wife

95
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,070
doing lately?

96
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:05,680
Good.

97
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,600
That's good.

98
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,010
A toast to you, Ms. Jian.

99
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,930
Nice to meet you.

100
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:18,680
Ms. Jian, you look better than ever.

101
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:22,190
Good thing you didn't end up with Lu Fan.

102
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,760
Look at the Lu family.

103
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,680
They're finished.

104
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,510
Exactly.

105
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:29,090
I heard Lu Fan is hiding
from debt collectors

106
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,360
like a stray dog.

107
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:33,159
He doesn't deserve someone like you.

108
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,600
Mr. Jian, you were far-sighted

109
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,800
and cut your losses in time.

110
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,190
You're so wise.

111
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,720
It's all in the past.

112
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,600
Let's forget it.

113
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,000
Thanks.

114
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,750
Master Jian,

115
00:07:46,270 --> 00:07:47,360
the food is ready.

116
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:51,750
Take your seats, everyone.

117
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:53,040
This way.

118
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,250
Who are you looking for?

119
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,180
What are you doing?

120
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,330
Lu Fan, what are you doing?

121
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:09,830
Don't move, or I'll strangle her!

122
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,950
I've given everything I had

123
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,750
to help you rise.

124
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,810
And what did you do?

125
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,690
You colluded with an outsider to set me up

126
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,800
and destroy Lu Group. Why?

127
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,360
You lied to me for ten years.

128
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:26,830
Why?

129
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,760
Lu Fan, are you crazy?

130
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,160
Let her go!

131
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,240
We can talk.

132
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,080
Xi.

133
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:48,320
Lu Fan, you want to know why?

134
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,550
I stayed by your side for 10 years.

135
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,030
Tell me,

136
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,360
have you ever seen me

137
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,150
as your fiancée?

138
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,270
What am I?

139
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,080
What am I to you?

140
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:08,200
I was a pet you could command at will,

141
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:12,600
an ornament to elevate your status!

142
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,550
You pitied me and offered me help,

143
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,910
so we

144
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:21,030
had to live in your shadow every day!

145
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,240
We were scared.

146
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,790
We were afraid

147
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,510
you'd get angry to throw us away

148
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:27,000
like trash!

149
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:28,720
Xi...

150
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:34,600
This isn't help.

151
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,790
It's humiliation.

152
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,360
And Su Xia.

153
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,910
You told me you were taking revenge.

154
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:42,890
But in reality,

155
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,150
it was betrayal!

156
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,790
You were cheating on me!

157
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,200
Yes, I deceived you.

158
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:55,080
But isn't ten years of my youth

159
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,550
enough to pay off what I owe you?

160
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,150
Why is Su Xia

161
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:01,670
better than me?

162
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:04,510
Lu Fan.

163
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:09,030
All I want is to see you

164
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:11,240
humiliated and abandoned like a dog.

165
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,600
Now,

166
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:18,320
get out of my house.

167
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:19,200
Get out!

168
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,320
We're getting married soon.

169
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,840
Getting married?

170
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,600
Xi...

171
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,510
Lu Fan, let me tell you one more thing.

172
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,650
Do you actually believe...

173
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,320
Do you actually believe

174
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,750
Su Xia is an angel who wants to save you?

175
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:51,320
She is the best-hidden

176
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,910
and deadliest pawn

177
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,150
Xiao Qi placed by your side.

178
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,630
You're lying.

179
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,790
Whether it's true or not

180
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,360
doesn't really matter to me.

181
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,200
I just want

182
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,870
to wake you up

183
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,390
for the sake of our past,

184
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,960
so you don't die a fool.

185
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,200
If you want to seek revenge

186
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,240
and take back what's yours,

187
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:14,390
go ahead.

188
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,030
Do you think

189
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,030
you're still that proud

190
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:24,320
and powerful Mr. Lu?

191
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:33,630
Get out of my house now.

192
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,750
Okay.

193
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:40,670
I swear

194
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:44,550
I'll take back everything

195
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,670
I've lost.
